    dc:description "FIGURES 1–3. Habitus photographs of Zherikhinia matobai sp. nov.—1, lateral, male (holotype); 2, dorsal, male (holotype); 3, dorsal, female (paratype, from, Ishigaki Is., Okinawa Pref.). Scale=1.0 mm." ;
